&lt;Discovery West Corp> said it plans tosell convertible subordinated notes in a principal amount ofbetween four mln and seven mln dlrs by way of a privateplacement through First Marathon Securities Ltd.    Discovery West said the notes will be convertible intoeight pct convertible subordinated debentures, which in turnwill be convertible into common shares at a price of two dlrs ashare.    It said it expects to complete the note sale on April nineand plans to use up to five mln dlrs of proceeds to buyconvertible notes of &lt;Rayrock Yellowknife Resources Inc>. Reuter&#3;